data.description: Welcome to your 2 bedroom, 1 bath abode! Situated on a charming corner lot, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. With a fenced yard, you'll have plenty of space for outdoor activities or relaxing under the sun. Park your car hassle-free in the 1 car garage, keeping it shielded from the elements. And that's not all! This gem is conveniently located near schools and shopping centers, ensuring that you're never far from what you need. Experience the joy of a well-planned home in a prime location.
